Report of the 2022 EUR Open Science Survey

Dr. Lizette Guzman-Ramirez, Dr. Antonio Schettino

2022-05-26

Introduction

Respondents

A total of 202 respondents started the survey, and 159 completed it (78.71%).

Considering only the completed surveys, Figure 1 shows the percentage of respondents as a function of school and position. Table 1 shows the percentage of respondents relative to the total number of employees

Figure 1: Response rate per school and position.

Table 1: Response rate per school relative to total staff. Source: EUR Annual Report 2020, Appendix 4
School respondents total staff percentage of respondents
ESSB 50 460 32.26%

ESHCC 8 166 5.16%
Note: According to the EUR Annual Report 2020, ESL has 351 employees but the survey was sent to 244 of them.
